      hook: "This is the final lesson of Rwendo's shona-english curriculum. 100 lessons. 10 modules. And this one — lesson 100 — is yours. Today you don't learn. Today you speak.",
      cultural_note: "Completing this curriculum means you've absorbed not just vocabulary but culture — tsika (respect), ubuntu, sadza and proverbs and moyo. You have not just learned Shona words. You have touched Shona life. That is the Rwendo journey.",
